WHO WE ARE
GCP Capital Partners (“GCP”) manages several North American private equity funds that have invested approximately $1.3 billion in over 50 portfolio companies. GCP’s realized investments have generated over $2.5 billion in proceeds. The funds make investments in financial technology/services, business services and energy companies.










